                    <div class="boxgrid-tall">
                        <div class="boxgrid-cbg" style="background-image: url('/static/img/cn99banner.webp');">
                            <div class="boxgrid-top">
                                <div class="boxgrid-top-price subheading"></div>
                                <h4 class="subheading"><span class="mdi ico-12px"></span> </h4>
                                <h3>Charlesn99</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="boxgrid-bottom">
                            <h6 class="subheading"><span>Open Source Community Manager</span></h6>
                            <p>I am Charles, a high school student who is an active tech and science enthusiast. I am new to the world of programming, but I am determined to learn new languages. I am currently learning HTML and Javascript. </p>
                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="boxgrid-bttns">
                            <a href="https://github.com/Charlesn99" class="button button-dark boxgrid-bttnc">GitHub <span class="mdi mdi-github ico-16px"></span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contentdiv cd-type-0">
                <h1 class="heading"><%- __('about.contributors.header') %></h1>
                <h2 class="subheading"><%- __('about.contributors.subheader') %></h2>
